Hyde Park Live is a live album by The Rolling Stones, released in 2013.
It was recorded at Hyde Park, London on July 6 and 13, 2013 during the
band's 50 and Counting Tour. The album was released exclusively as a
digital download through iTunes on July 22, 2013 for a limited time of
four weeks. The album debuted at #16 in the UK and #19 in the US
